---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Codulent AI Automation Consulting"
  description="Learn about Codulent's mission to help businesses automate operations with AI. Based in Austin, TX, serving clients nationwide."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-900 via-navy-800 to-navy-700 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-accent-400 font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide uppercase mb-4">About Codulent</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white">
        Making AI work for real businesses
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We bridge the gap between cutting-edge AI technology and everyday business operations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg text-slate-600 space-y-5">
          <p>
            Codulent started as a product design and manufacturing consulting firm, helping entrepreneurs bring physical products from concept to reality. We spent years solving complex engineering challenges, managing supply chains, and delivering tangible results.
          </p>
          <p>
            But as AI technology advanced, we saw a new and arguably more transformative opportunity: <strong class="text-navy-800">helping businesses automate their operations</strong>. The same problem-solving mindset that guided product development now drives our approach to AI automation — understanding the real-world workflow, designing a practical solution, and delivering measurable outcomes.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, Codulent is focused entirely on AI automation consulting. We help businesses of all sizes onboard AI tools — from configuring OpenClaw to automate email processing and task management, to building comprehensive automation strategies that reduce manual work and free teams to focus on high-value activities.
          </p>
          <p>
            We're not here to sell you hype. We're here to roll up our sleeves, understand your operations, and implement AI solutions that genuinely save time and money.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-navy-900">How we work</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-500">
          Our values shape every engagement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17 17.25 21A2.652 2.652 0 0 0 21 17.25l-5.877-5.877M11.42 15.17l2.496-3.03c.317-.384.74-.626 1.208-.766M11.42 15.17l-4.655 5.653a2.548 2.548 0 1 1-3.586-3.586l6.837-5.63m5.108-.233c.55-.164 1.163-.188 1.743-.14a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 4.486-6.336l-3.276 3.277a3.004 3.004 0 0 1-2.25-2.25l3.276-3.276a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-6.336 4.486c.048.58.024 1.194-.14 1.743" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">Practical Results</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We focus on solutions that deliver measurable impact. Every recommendation is grounded in your specific business context, not theoretical ideals.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 5.25a3 3 0 0 1 3 3m3 0a6 6 0 0 1-7.029 5.912c-.563-.097-1.159.026-1.563.43L10.5 17.25H8.25v2.25H6v2.25H2.25v-2.818c0-.597.237-1.17.659-1.591l6.499-6.499c.404-.404.527-1 .43-1.563A6 6 0 1 1 21.75 8.25Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">Hands-On Implementation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            We don't just hand you a strategy deck and walk away. We build, configure, test, and deploy the automation alongside your team.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 8.25h9m-9 3H12m-9.75 1.51c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.129.166 2.27.293 3.423.379.35.026.67.21.865.501L12 21l2.755-4.133a1.14 1.14 0 0 1 .865-.501 48.172 48.172 0 0 0 3.423-.379c1.584-.233 2.707-1.626 2.707-3.228V6.741c0-1.602-1.123-2.995-2.707-3.228A48.394 48.394 0 0 0 12 3c-2.392 0-4.744.175-7.043.513C3.373 3.746 2.25 5.14 2.25 6.741v6.018Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">Honest Guidance</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            If something won't benefit from AI, we'll tell you. Our goal is to earn your trust through transparency and delivering only what adds real value.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Location -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-navy-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy-900 mb-4">Based in Austin, TX</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          We work with businesses nationwide. Whether you're local or remote, our consulting and implementation process is designed to be fully effective regardless of location.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center px-7 py-3.5 rounded-lg bg-navy-700 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-navy-800 transition-colors"
        >
          Let's Talk
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
